title.narrative: ENHANCED QUALITY OF EDUCATION FOR IMPROVED LEARNING OUTCOMES.

description.narrative: Children, from early childhood to adolescence, including vulnerable children, have enhanced quality of education for improved learning outcomes., which contributes to Early Childhood Development, Learning Outcomes. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Evaluations, Research And Data, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Girls and boys, in particular the most marginalized and those affected by humanitarian crises, are provided with inclusive and equitable qualityeducation and learning opportunities.
